}. * {{ill|Otomo no Otomaro|ja|大伴安麻呂|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtomo no Yasumaro|qq=}} - Recognized in the 13th year of Emperor Tenmu's reign (684). * {{ill|Kose no Kurohito|ja|巨勢黒麻呂|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kose no Kurohito|qq=}} - Middle counselor (chūnagon).
